{"tid":1229174,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【改歌】《致所有對逝者不敬之人》","createTime":"2019-06-15T23:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T11:14:40.000Z","uid":41326,"like":130,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d721643920efa37e6ca7c5d5740db7a23dd53699","tid":1229174,"uid":41326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:48:13.000Z","msg":"歌：<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rQv1kD0lYAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrQv1kD0lYAA&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhqf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=524e0da8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rQv1kD0lYAA</a><br />\n<br />\n尋日有一位最值得尊敬嘅巴打離開咗我地。<br />\n網上有好多評論都令人覺得好心寒。<br />\n點解有一堆人可以對逝者嘅事討論得如此涼薄？<br />\n<br />\n根本無人有資格質疑佢嘅爭取方式值得與否。<br />\n無人有資格質疑佢嘅動機。<br />\n無人有資格對佢指手畫腳。<br />\n<br />\n因為佢付出嘅比我地所有人付出嘅都多。"},{"pid":"a71149e8b125b46a03faa26bc6717dac379c5b09","tid":1229174,"uid":227470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:55:42.000Z","msg":"啱啊～"},{"pid":"549fd7f02153d0665c2a3b1c3453c812169e39f7","tid":1229174,"uid":41326,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:08:32.000Z","msg":"有人話佢蠢；<br />\n有人話唔值；<br />\n有人話早死早著真係好；<br />\n有人話抵死；<br />\n有人話佢喺半空嗰陣一定好後悔；<br />\n有人話無保險賠；<br />\n有人話佢失足唔怪得人；<br />\n有人話佢收咗錢做死士；<br />\n有人話佢想死好耐；<br />\n有人話一個唔夠；<br />\n有人話死咗唔洗買樓；<br />\n<br />\n原來政見不同或者政治冷感就可以連血都變冷埋。<br />\n我懷疑講得出上面說話嘅生物根本唔係人。"},{"pid":"b1a3f966825fa5b54cdd5410c29c958b42eb7f47","tid":1229174,"uid":34503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:09:25.000Z","msg":"挽歌兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95385e01b1b3a86e73a30ea62606d123e75c9bb3","tid":1229174,"uid":41326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1a3f966825fa5b54cdd5410c29c958b42eb7f47","tid":1229174,"uid":34503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:09:25.000Z","msg":"挽歌兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" clas